Class 45 Peak Diesel Locomotive

Type 4 Diesel Electric locomotive used by British Railways

Four Type variations including:
- Split Headcode
- Centre Headcode
- No Headcode
- No Headcode with Headlamp
- BR Blue Liveries
- BR Green Liveries

Authentic Sounds
Selection of Names
Full Custom Cab

Five interesting scenarios:
- Graveyard Shift
- Newcastle Broon
- Derby v Reading
- Port Road Peak
- Reading Semi Fast

This pack is equivalent to the class 45 Peak from STEAM Plus the late model expansion
